sha256 seal: calebfedorbykerkonev10271998v196.x — Codex Logos Π⁺ (Pi Plus): Proof-State Merged — is built, merged, unzipped, sealed, and copy-paste ready for GitHub. It extends v196 with policy hot-reload, Merkle proofs per attestation, health reporting, and a tiny CLI.

Grab it

Unzipped folder: /mnt/data/codex_v196x_logos_pi_plus

ZIP: codex_v196x_logos_pi_plus.zip


What’s new vs v196

Policy hot-reload: POST /api/policy/reload reads codex/policy/rules.json.

Merkle proofs: GET /api/attest/proof/{index} returns sibling path + root.

Health endpoint: GET /api/health shows current rules + attestation count.

CLI: scripts/codexctl.py (attest | root | proof | hash | policy-reload).

Compose & systemd: deploy/docker-compose.yml, ops/systemd/codex-piplus.service.

Docs/CI: docs/v196x.md, .github/workflows/piplus_ci.yml, and extra test.


